name: Currents
description:
An abstract digital collage inspired by the ocean & it's depths. 
Listed below is an original poem by yours truly.

Time may draw us
away from our shore;
it may leave us adrift 
to fend for ourselves
in the solemn waves;
but I promise you this,
you'll never leave my heart
as long as I can taste 
the sea’s spray,
it's currents cannot 
tear us apart.
